# Datasets and generated evaluation files
VOCdevkit/
/datasets/
!docs/datasets/
!docs/datasets/*.md
Medical_Datasets/
miou_out/

# Model weights should be published through Releases or external storage.
*.pth
*.pt
*.onnx
model_data/*
!model_data/README.md
